
Overview of noun halo

The noun halo has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                           
1. (4) aura, aureole, halo, nimbus, glory, gloriole -- (an indication of radiant light drawn around the head of a saint)
2. ring, halo, annulus, doughnut, anchor ring -- (a toroidal shape; "a ring of ships in the harbor"; "a halo of smoke")
3. halo -- (a circle of light around the sun or moon)
